data.description: Wow Check out this HUGE SUPER clean home! Located in the desirable Bay River Colony, this home offers 5 HUGE full bedrooms 3.5 full baths plus game room and study upstairs! Good as new, lightly lived in. Open concept living, dining and kitchen. Gorgeous granite counters in the kitchen! Kitchen breakfast bar perfect for the kids. Granite, tile backsplash, SS appliances, gas range. Plenty of cabinets and pantry space. Kitchen has a breakfast table area overlooking the backyard. Extensive 18'' ceramic tile floors, 2''faux wood blinds, ceiling fans. Primary bedroom down with garden tub/shower bath, double vanity sinks & HUGE walk-in closet. 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and utility up. The Seller is leaving the shed in the backyard for the new homeowners. Low taxes. Family friendly community offers 2 parks, great schools, near I-10, & close to all the shopping, restaurants and entertainment amenities! Easy commute to Houston or Beaumont! Don't miss out on this Baytown Beauty!
